theorem closure_interior_iterate_two {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    (Function.iterate (fun S : Set X => closure (interior S)) 2) A =
      closure (interior A) := by
  simp [Function.iterate,
        Topology.closure_interior_idempotent (X := X) (A := A)]

theorem closure_interior_idempotent_six {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure
        (interior
          (closure
            (interior
              (closure
                (interior
                  (closure
                    (interior
                      (closure
                        (interior
                          (closure
                            (interior
                              (closure A))))))))))) =
      closure (interior A) := by
  simp [Topology.closure_interior_idempotent]

theorem interior_inter_closure_eq_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    (A : Set X) :
    interior (A : Set X) ∩ closure A = interior A := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hx
    exact hx.1
  · intro hxInt
    have hxA : x ∈ (A : Set X) := interior_subset hxInt
    have hxCl : x ∈ closure (A : Set X) := subset_closure hxA
    exact ⟨hxInt, hxCl⟩
